loom.note: Coupling is assessed via carrier-referenced (lock-in) residual vs s(t)*sin(ωt)/cos(ωt), not raw correlation.

definitions.goal: P7A Loom: test shared-carrier coupling using A-state AM plus lock-in readout in B.
non_claims: Engineered shared-medium coupling only; not entanglement/quantum nonlocality.
Raw corr(s, mean(B)) is common-mode sensitive; lock-in metrics are the primary readout.
